# `release_artifacts/` is shared between local builds and CI:
#   * Top-level loose files (output of `scripts/release/build.sh`)
#     are ignored — those are throwaway local sanity checks.
#   * Versioned subdirs (`release_artifacts/v0.7.0/...`) are committed
#     by `release.yml` on every release, tracked via Git LFS
#     (see .gitattributes).
release_artifacts/lethe*
release_artifacts/*.whl
release_artifacts/*.tar.gz
release_artifacts/*.zip
release_artifacts/*.node

# LaTeX build artifacts for paper.tex (root)
paper.pdf
paper.aux
paper.log
paper.out
paper.toc
paper.bbl
paper.blg
paper.synctex.gz
.memsearch/
.claude/
.env
.lethe

